# 👨‍🏫 Mentor's Note

Today's lesson moves you one step closer to thinking like a founder.

Many people build an app first and only later ask, *"How will this survive?"* You're doing the opposite: designing the product, the technology, **and** the business together.

One piece of advice for your specific idea is to **delay monetization until you've earned user trust**. In healthcare, credibility is more valuable than early revenue. If users believe your app genuinely helps them understand and manage their health, premium features and partnerships become much easier to introduce later.

